### Hello World

My name is Mai, a 25 years old designer Ho Chi Minh city, Vietnam. I love Graphic Design; I'm passionate about creativity and making life more beautiful. Most of my projects focus on Business Identity and Branding, Print Media and Web Design. I have a desire to develop and progress my skill without any stops.

I'm available for hire: full-time, part-time, or freelance gigs.
